comments: Jokic (DEN) initiates marginal contact with Wright (DAL) during his drive.
Powell (DAL) grabs Murray's (DEN) jersey and affects his driving shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) and Doncic (DAL) make incidental contact during the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) and Wright (DAL) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Finney-Smith (DAL) makes contact with Grant's (DEN) arm and affects his shot attempt.
Harris (DEN) makes marginal contact with Hardaway Jr. (DAL) before the screen.
Wright (DAL) makes marginal contact with Murray's (DEN) off-arm before Finney-Smith (DAL) blocks the shot attempt.
Harris (DEN) moves alongside Doncic (DAL) and maintains a legal guarding position on his drive to the basket.  Doncic loses his balance on the spin move.
Powell (DAL) sets the screen on Harris (DEN) and absorbs the contact.
Harris (DEN) and Powell (DAL) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Plumlee (DEN) extends his arm into Doncic (DAL) and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) sets the screen on Powell (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Finney-Smith (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Jokic (DEN) during the drive.
Kleber (DAL) sets the screen on Grant (DEN) and absorbs the contact.
